<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>What<sp/>is<sp/>RAM</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">RAM<sp/>is<sp/>the<sp/>memory,<sp/>the<sp/>storage<sp/>space,<sp/>where<sp/>the<sp/>blockchain<sp/>stores<sp/>data.<sp/>If<sp/>your<sp/>contract<sp/>needs<sp/>to<sp/>store<sp/>data<sp/>on<sp/>the<sp/>blockchain,<sp/>like<sp/>in<sp/>a<sp/>database,<sp/>then<sp/>it<sp/>can<sp/>store<sp/>it<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>blockchain&apos;s<sp/>RAM<sp/>using<sp/>either<sp/>a<sp/>`multi-index<sp/>table`<sp/>or<sp/>a<sp/>`singleton`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
